        "subject": "LU-11763 lnet: Add warning message in \"lctl network configure\"",
        "message": "LU-11763 lnet: Add warning message in \"lctl network configure\"\n\nCurrently, if the network interface is not specified\nin the modprobe.conf file, then the \"lctl network configure\"\ncommand configures network using default interface values for\nsocklnd and o2iblnd.\n\nStarting Lustre 2.13 release, it will be necessary to\nspecify network interface to configure network using\n\"lctl network configure\" command.\n\nLustre-change: https://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/33835/\nLustre-commit: a7c3caa2f38090a0658aead4587102f27f5d1ab0\n\nChange-Id: I3e3d8fac5f9837330d8787f36826ef9b2b4ea93e\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Sonia Sharma <sharmaso@whamcloud.com>\nSigned-off-by: Minh Diep <mdiep@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_10"
    }
